<plot>A group of friends travel across town one night in search of a party. What begins as a straight forward drive soon becomes an urban odyssey. Altercations at the video shop, arguments at the news-agent, disagreements with drug-dealers, banter in the back-seat and run-ins with the local police all combine to create a moving and memorable story of youth finding its way one winter's night in Brighton.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?579359</url></doc>
